'''1940年南卡罗莱纳飓风'''（{{lang-en|1940 South Carolina hurricane}}）是1940年8月11至12日袭击[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]和[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]沿海地区的二级飓风。气旋在[[背风群岛_(加勒比海)|背风群岛]]北面成型并向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]移动，从[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]东侧经过后继续向西北偏西逼近[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]。风暴中心[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]美国，登陆点附近及北侧沿海地区预先收到飓风警告。南卡罗莱纳州海岸沿线测得约4米的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]，[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]北部降雨量普遍在380毫米以上。气旋向东南面缓慢移动，在此期间逐渐减弱，之后转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，乔治亚州、南卡罗莱纳州、[[田纳西州|田纳西州]]和[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]发生重大洪灾和[[山崩|山体滑坡]]。北卡罗莱纳州发生的山体滑坡属百年一遇水平，整场飓风一共造成50人遇难，损失总额达到1300万美元{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，所有损失金额均为1940年美元价值。|group="注"}}。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|1940 Atlantic hurricane 3 track.png}}
8月5日，早间[[天气图|天气图]]显示[[圣马丁岛_(加勒比海)|圣马丁岛]]和[[圣托马斯岛_(美属维尔京群岛)|圣托马斯岛]]之间有弱[[热带扰动|扰动天气]]存在<ref name="mwr">{{cite report | url = https://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/068/mwr-068-08-0217.pdf | title = Tropical Disturbances of August 1940 | year = 1940 | author = Jean H. Galenne | publisher = American Meteorological Society | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303232446/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/068/mwr-068-08-0217.pdf | deadurl = no | pages = 217–218 | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  | access-date = 2017-01-06 }}</ref>。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]下午18点，[[英属维尔京群岛|英属维尔京群岛]]的[[阿内加达岛|阿内加达岛]]西北偏西方向约48公里海域发展出热带低气压<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

气旋朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]靠近[[莫纳海峡|莫纳海峡]]，在[[波多黎各|波多黎各]][[圣胡安_(波多黎各)|圣胡安]]产生时速71公里的阵骤风。8月6日，正在发展的风暴逼近[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]东南部并产生中到大浪。气旋从巴哈马东南部附近经过后转向北上，到8月10日已有船只测得飓风强度风力。8月11日下午，风暴从南卡罗莱纳州[[博福特_(南卡罗莱纳州)|博福特]]附近登陆并朝内陆移动，于当天17至18点在[[萨凡纳|萨凡纳]]东北方向不远处经过。萨凡纳所测最高风速为每小时117公里，最低[[气压|气压]]975[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.78[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]），是当地[[1911年大西洋飓风季|29年来]]遇到的最强飓风。<ref name="Tannehill">{{cite book | author = Ivan Ray Tannehill | title = Hurricanes | publisher = Princeton University Press | year = 1943 | pages = 250–251}}</ref>萨凡纳和[[查尔斯顿_(南卡罗来纳州)|查尔斯顿]]之间地区风力达到飓风标准。气旋当晚减弱成热带风暴，之后四至五天以弱热带风暴强度在内陆蜿蜒行进，最终于8月14日晚转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。<ref name="HURDAT" />

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:August_1940_rainfall.png|thumb]]
面对气旋逼近，气象机构于8月7至9日发出公告，建议巴哈马东部和西大西洋亚热带海域的小型船只提高警惕<ref>{{cite web | url = https://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/dwm/1940/19400807.djvu | author = United States Weather Bureau | title = Daily Weather Maps: August 7, 1940 | date = 1940-08-07 | accessdate = 2017-01-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20041114102500/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/dwm/1940/19400807.djvu | publisher = United States Department of Commerce | archivedate = 2004-11-14 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author-link = 美国国家气象局 | url = https://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/dwm/1940/19400808.djvu | author = United States Weather Bureau | title = Daily Weather Maps: August 8, 1940 | date = 1940-08-08 | accessdate = 2017-01-06 | publisher = United States Department of Commerce | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303171119/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/dwm/1940/19400808.djvu | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/dwm/1940/19400809.djvu | author = United States Weather Bureau | title = Daily Weather Maps: August 9, 1940 | date = 1940-08-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303205116/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/dwm/1940/19400809.djvu | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2017-01-06 | publisher = [[美国商务部|United States Department of Commerce]] | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。截至8月10日上午9点半，小型船只警告的生效范围已经包括巴哈马最北端，以及[[迈阿密|迈阿密]]至[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]][[哈特拉斯角_(北卡罗莱纳州)|哈特拉斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Hatteras}}）之间的[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]沿海地区<ref>{{cite web | url = https://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/dwm/1940/19400810.djvu | author = United States Weather Bureau | title = Daily Weather Maps: August 10, 1940 | date = 1940-08-10 | accessdate = 2017-01-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303190918/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/dwm/1940/19400810.djvu | publisher = United States Department of Commerce | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。到了8月11日早上，北卡罗莱纳州[[威尔明顿_(北卡罗莱纳州)|威尔明顿]]向北至哈特拉斯角，以及萨凡纳至佛罗里达州[[费南迪纳比奇_(佛罗里达州)|费南迪纳比奇]]收到风暴警告。萨凡纳向北至威尔明顿则接获飓风警告<ref>{{cite web | url = https://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/dwm/1940/19400811.djvu | author = United States Weather Bureau | title = Daily Weather Maps: August 11, 1940 | date = 1940-08-11 | accessdate = 2017-01-06 | publisher = United States Department of Commerce | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221722/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/dwm/1940/19400811.djvu | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。8月12日，所有沿海地区的警告均停止生效<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221722/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/dwm/1940/19400811.djvu | deadurl = no | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/dwm/1940/19400811.djvu | author = United States Weather Bureau | title = Daily Weather Maps: August 12, 1940 | date = 1940-08-12 | accessdate = 2017-01-07 | publisher = United States Department of Commerce | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。

南卡罗莱纳州海岸沿线测得近四米高的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]<ref>{{cite web | author = Stephen P. Leatherman | page = 213 | url = https://www.nap.edu/read/1993/chapter/13#213 | publisher = Commission on Engineering and Technical Systems | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160816140206/http://www.nap.edu/read/1993/chapter/13#213 | title = Hurricane Hugo, Puerto Rico, the Virgin Islands, and Charleston, South Carolina, September 17–22, 1989 | year = 1994 | accessdate = 2017-01-06 | archivedate = 2016-08-16 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[查尔斯顿_(南卡罗莱纳州)|查尔斯顿]]因气旋遭受价值150万美元的破坏，乔治亚州萨凡纳也受到100万美元损失。沿海地区的损失总额达到300万美元。乔治亚州有两人丧生，但其中一人死于恐懼引發的心脏衰竭。<ref name="mwr" />距登陆点不远的博福特在24小时内共降下275毫米雨量<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.dnr.sc.gov/climate/sco/Tropics/hurricanes_affecting_sc.php | title = South Carolina Hurricane Climatology | author = South Carolina State Climatology Office | year = 2009 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161230224755/http://www.dnr.sc.gov/climate/sco/Tropics/hurricanes_affecting_sc.php | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-12-30 | accessdate = 2017-01-07 | publisher = South Carolina Department of Natural Resources }}</ref>。乔治亚州以[[杰佛逊县_(乔治亚州)|杰佛逊县]]的[[路易斯维尔_(乔治亚州)|路易斯维尔]]（{{lang|en|Louisville}}）降水最多，达347毫米；南卡罗莱纳州则以查尔斯顿最高，有322毫米<ref name="WPCSE">{{cite book | last = Roth | first = David M | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Point Maxima | chapter = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall in the Southeastern United States | author2 = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcsoutheast.html | accessdate = 2017-01-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070229/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcsoutheast.html }}</ref>。飓风登陆点附近的沿海地区有不少人员丧生，早期新闻报导称有35人遇难。据《每月天气回顾》（{{lang|en|Monthly Weather Review}}）记载，由于飓风警告和疏散工作及时，死亡人数并不高。但现代研究结果又表明整场风暴共夺走50条人命。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/NWS-TPC-5.pdf | page = 7 | author = Eric S. Blake | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161221141759/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/NWS-TPC-5.pdf | archivedate = 2016-12-21 | author2 = Edward N. Rappaport | author3 = Christopher W. Landsea | title = NOAA Technical Memorandum NWS TPC-5: The Deadliest, Costliest, and Most Intense United States Tropical Cyclones From 1851 to 2006 (and Other Frequently Requested Hurricane Facts) | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2007-04-15 | accessdate = 2017-01-07 | deadurl = no | format = PDF }}</ref>

离开沿海地区后，气旋逐渐消散，在此期间继续降下暴雨，引起严重山洪暴发并导致重大破坏，南、北卡罗莱纳州、田纳西州和乔治亚州北部大部分地区被淹。北卡罗莱纳州西部的降水普遍超过380毫米，最高降雨量达525毫米。<ref name="WPCSE" />北卡罗莱纳州西部山区发生大量[[山崩|山体滑坡]]事故，频次之高达百年一遇水平<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.geology.enr.state.nc.us/Geologic_hazards_cost/costs.htm | title = Geologic hazards: Dates, Level of Events, Damage and Indirect Costs | publisher = North Carolina Geological Survey | author = Richard Wooten | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090511110250/http://www.geology.enr.state.nc.us/Geologic_hazards_cost/costs.htm | deadurl = yes | date = 2004-08 | accessdate = 2009-05-11 | archivedate = 2009-05-11 }}</ref>。田纳西州东部和北卡罗莱纳州西部的铁路受到重创，只能暂停运作<ref>{{cite book | isbn = 978-0-8078-5625-3 | accessdate = 2017-01-07 | year = 2005 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=oTEt2I1neQIC&pg=PA121&lpg=PA121&dq=hurricane+rainfall+august+1940+north+carolina&source=bl&ots=fWMI10te_y&sig=Ey_lk-UptEQaKe9iN19DfWUEfaw&hl=en&ei=VMY6SvnRE4zKMt-R8a8F&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3#v=onepage&q=hurric | title = North Carolina weather & climate | author = Peter John Robinson | page = 121 | publisher = University of North Carolina Press}}</ref>。威尔森溪（{{lang|en|Wilson Creek}}）位于[[考德威尔县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|考德威尔县]]阿达科（{{lang|en|Adako}}）附近河段流量估计高达每秒2800立方米<ref>{{cite web | date = 2008-10-14 | accessdate = 2017-01-07 | author-link = 美国地质调查局 | url = https://pubs.usgs.gov/sir/2008/5164/pdf/sir20085164_WilsonCreek.pdf | title = Wilson Creek near Adako, North Carolina | pages = 149–150 | author = United States Geological Survey | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231654/http://pubs.usgs.gov/sir/2008/5164/pdf/sir20085164_WilsonCreek.pdf | deadurl = no | format = PDF }}</ref>。[[沃托加县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|沃托加县]]的迪普加普（{{lang|en|Deep Gap}}）发生强烈碎屑流，导致26人丧生<ref>{{cite web | title = Geologic hazards in North Carolina — Landslides | author = North Carolina Geological Survey | url = http://www.geology.enr.state.nc.us/Landslide_Info/Landslides_example_historical_events.htm | date = 2008-02-19 | accessdate = 2013-01-28 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130128084049/http://www.geology.enr.state.nc.us/Landslide_Info/Landslides_example_historical_events.htm | archivedate = 2013-01-28 }}</ref>。全县大部分地区同外界的交通中断两周之久。碎屑流和洪水致使[[421号美国国道|421号美国国道]]位于迪普加普和[[威尔克斯县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|威尔克斯县]]枫树泉（{{lang|en|Maple Springs}}）间约9600米路段有21处中断，考德威尔县九成桥梁毁于洪灾。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://wncsos.blogspot.com/2008/03/laurelmor-and-landslides.html | title = Laurelmor and Landslides | date = 2008-03-05 | accessdate = 2017-01-07 | publisher = Western North Carolina Landslide Advisory Website | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160807182848/http://wncsos.blogspot.com/2008/03/laurelmor-and-landslides.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-08-07 }}</ref>新闻报导称有30人在洪灾中遇难，损失数额超过1000万美元<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Millsboro Daily News | date = 1940-08-16 | title = Floods Surge Toward Surge}}</ref>。

气旋于8月13日从西侧进入[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]并开始产生降雨。该州南部和西部多地发生洪灾，[[汉普顿锚地|汉普顿锚地]]测得121毫米雨量。全州以[[弗洛伊德县_(弗吉尼亚州)|弗洛伊德县]]科伯山（{{lang|en|Copper Hill}}）雨量最高，达433毫米。<ref name="Mid Atl">{{cite book | author = Roth, David M | author2 = Weather Prediction Center | year = 2012 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060511/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmidatl.html | deadurl = no | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Point Maxima | chapter = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall in the Mid-Atlantic United States | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | accessdate = 2017-01-07 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmidatl.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>8月17日，梅赫林河（{{lang|en|Meherrin River}}）位于[[恩波里亚_(维吉尼亚州)|恩波里亚]]境内河段洪峰创下新纪录，高达9.6米，比洪水水位还高2.6米。多条山区河流泛滥成灾，将桥梁冲毁并引起山体滑坡，导致道路封堵。[[诺福克_(弗吉尼亚州)|诺福克]]、弗吉尼亚州西南部及[[阿什维尔|阿什维尔]]地区的多条公路封闭。8月13日，[[威斯特摩兰县_(弗吉尼亚州)|威斯特摩兰县]]科尔斯角（{{lang|en|Coles Point}}）上游约八公里处发生的[[螺杆压缩机|油压机]]碰撞事故可能也是由这场风暴引起。<ref>{{cite book | last = Roth | first = David M | title = Virginia Hurricane History: Early Twentieth Century | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/roth/vaerly20hur.htm | year = 1999 | accessdate = 2017-01-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160114150253/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/roth/vaerly20hur.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-01-14 }}</ref>

